# Rewards Engine API

Backend API for managing customer accounts, purchase transactions, points ledger tracking, rewards, and redemptions.

## Status

In Progress

## Current Features

- ASP.NET Core Web API
- Swagger/OpenAPI testing
- SQLite database with Entity Framework Core
- Customer creation, update, deactivation, and reactivation
- Purchase transaction processing
- Duplicate transaction protection
- Points calculation from purchases
- Ledger-based points tracking
- Customer points balance lookup
- Reward creation
- Reward redemption
- Points deduction through negative ledger entries
- Promotion creation and management
- Active promotion filtering by start/end date
- Category-based multiplier promotions
- Bonus point calculation during transaction processing

## API Areas

- Customers
- Transactions
- Points Ledger
- Rewards
- Redemptions

## Tech Stack

- C#
- ASP.NET Core
- Entity Framework Core
- SQLite
- Swagger/OpenAPI
